        "body": "## Summary\nThis PR adds only the intended Apr 18, Apr 19, and Apr 20 YouTube clone feature commits from Shambhavi's fixed fork into the clean AKRITI codebase.\n\n## Included commits\nApr 18:\n- f7aad72 feat: connect axios with json-server using useFetch\n- eb1c465 feat: add reusable video card component\n\nApr 19:\n- 55eb838 feat: implement comment section UI\n- 7a97e1b feat: add channel page and channel header\n\nApr 20:\n- 17e019b feat: implement home page video listing\n- 367a3eb feat: add watch page and video player integration\n- 7a6610b feat: wire search, library pages, and responsive layout updates\n\n## Excluded intentionally\n- Apr 21 duplicate commits\n- Apr 24 merge commits\n- Merge pull request #1\n- Merge pull request #2\n",
